### CCR-017 §2 — Table is_pause 직교 축 제약
###
### 검증:
### - LIVE + is_pause=true 허용 (브레이크/중재)
### - PAUSED + is_pause=false 거부 (불변 조합)
### - EMPTY/SETUP/CLOSED 상태에서 is_pause=true 거부

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 61.1 PATCH /tables/1 — LIVE + is_pause=true 허용
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "status": "live",
  "is_pause": true
}

# 예상: 200 OK (브레이크/중재 상태)

### 61.2 PATCH — PAUSED + is_pause=false (불변 조합)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "status": "paused",
  "is_pause": false
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# {
#   "error": "INVALID_STATE_COMBINATION",
#   "message": "PAUSED 상태는 is_pause=true 여야 합니다",
#   "allowed": { "status": "paused", "is_pause": true }
# }

### 61.3 PATCH — EMPTY + is_pause=true (불변 조합)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{
  "status": "empty",
  "is_pause": true
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "INVALID_STATE_COMBINATION", "message": "EMPTY/SETUP/CLOSED에서 is_pause=false 고정" }

### 61.4 GET /tables/1 — 응답에 is_pause 필드 포함
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "id": "tbl_01HVQK...",
#   "status": "live",
#   "is_pause": true,
#   ...
# }

### 61.5 WebSocket TableStatusChanged 이벤트 (수동)
###
### wscat -c 'ws://localhost:8000/ws/lobby?token=<jwt>&format=json'
### 위 61.1 요청 후 수신:
### {
###   "type": "TableStatusChanged",
###   "payload": {
###     "table_id": 1,
###     "old_status": "live",
###     "new_status": "live",
###     "old_is_pause": false,
###     "new_is_pause": true,
###     "reason": "break"
###   }
### }
